<h1 class="section-title" style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Join the Lab</h1>

<div class="join-content">
<p>
We are looking for motivated researchers at all career stages who share
our interest in evolutionary biology and computational approaches.
</p>

<h3 style="font-size: 1rem; margin: 1.5rem 0 0.75rem; color: #333;">Open Positions</h3>

<ul>
<li><strong>Undergrad students</strong> Internship</li>
<li><strong>MSc students</strong> thesis projects or internship</li>
<li><strong>PhD students</strong> </li>
<li><strong>Postdoctoral researchers</strong></li>
<li><strong>Research technicians</strong> and visiting scholars</li>
</ul>

<h3 style="font-size: 1rem; margin: 1.5rem 0 0.75rem; color: #333;">How to Apply</h3>

<p>
Interested candidates should send an email to <strong>alexandros.pittis@gmail.com</strong> or <strong>alexandros.pittis@imbb.forth.gr</strong> with:
</p>

<ul>
<li>Your CV</li>
<li>Briefly describing your motivation to join the lab</li>
</ul>

<h3 style="font-size: 1rem; margin: 1.5rem 0 0.75rem; color: #333;">Funding Opportunities</h3>

<p>
We can help identify funding opportunities for your stay, including:
</p>

<ul>
<li><a href="https://marie-sklodowska-curie-actions.ec.europa.eu/actions/postdoctoral-fellowships" target="_blank">Marie Skłodowska-Curie Postdoctoral Fellowships</a></li>
<li><a href="https://www.embo.org/funding/fellowships-grants-and-career-support/postdoctoral-fellowships/" target="_blank">EMBO Postdoctoral Fellowships</a></li>
<li><a href="https://www.embo.org/funding/fellowships-grants-and-career-support/scientific-exchange-grants/" target="_blank">EMBO Scientific Exchange Grants</a></li>
</ul>

</div>

